high_descs: Walk straight and then turn right to face the sink.
Pick pick up the spoon to the left of the knife on the sink.
Turn around, head towards the coffee maker, and then turn left to face the drawer on your right hand.
Pull out the drawer and place the spoon inside.
Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the other spoon on the sink.
Turn around, head towards the coffee maker, and then turn left to face the drawer on your right hand.
Pull out the drawer and place the spoon inside.
anns.task_desc: Place the two spoons in the drawer at the counter edge.

high_descs: Move to the left of the sink in front and to the right of you.
Pick up a spoon from the sink.
Move to the counter space behind you to the left of the stove.
Place the spoon inside the drawer farthest away from you and close the drawer.
Move to the sink to the left of you.
Pick up a spoon from the sink.
Move to the counter space behind you to the left of the stove.
Place the spoon inside the drawer farthest away from you and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoons from the sink in the drawer on the left farthest away on stove side.

high_descs: Walk straight in the kitchen and then turn right facing the sink
Pick up the metal spoon from the sink
Turn around to counter behind you
Open last drawer, place spoon inside and close back
Turn back around and face the kitchen sink
Pick up another metal spoon from the sink
Turn around to counter behind you
Open last drawer, place spoon inside and close back
anns.task_desc: Put clean spoon away in the drawer.

high_descs: Walk straight ahead toward the window to approach the sink on the right.
Pick up the spoon from the left side of the sink.
Turn directly around to approach the last drawer on your right under the counter.
Open the drawer, place the spoon inside and close the drawer.
Turn to your left and approach the sink again.
Pick up the last spoon on the counter.
Turn around and walk back to the same drawer you put the first spoon into.
Open the drawer and put the second spoon next to the first spoon and close the drawer again.
anns.task_desc: Put spoons away in the drawer.

high_descs: Go forward to the sink that will be on your right.
On the left side of the sink, pick up the spoon that is closest to the faucet.
Turn around and head to the cabinet with the toaster on it.
Open the drawer on the far left side of the cabinet, put the spoon inside, and close the drawer.
Turn around and head back to the sink.
On the left side of the sink, pick up the spoon.
Turn around and go back to the cabinet with the toaster on it.
Open the far left drawer, put the spoon inside, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons in a drawer.
